item.description: 30.September 2021 - Semi-live video session - “Cloud Stories from Norway, Episode 9: Frequent releases with Azure Kubernetes Service (AKS)” “Cloud stories from Norway” is a 40-minutes long videoshow where Microsoft Norway together with invited guests features Azure cloud best practices, patterns, tips & tricks used in production in the products and services of well-known Norwegian companies.
